TO run this change the image in image processor.py to whatever image you want to check for 
run this command 
for the first time use
verilator --binary -j 4 -Wno-fatal riscv_soc.v

then followed by 
./run_sim.sh

to know about the catergory the category with the highest value is the predicted category
the meaning of the catergory are
0 for plane
5 for dog
9 for truck

the rest are categories for which model was not trained for
